{"tid":958579,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(連登喜訊) 他殺了孕妻跟小孩 竟然收到全美國的情書","createTime":"2018-12-28T02:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T05:58:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0654fa82ae90588be507120f95995b8e63f63e60","tid":958579,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Hd02KroxPGWcMZWKoNRliA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/news_tvbs_com_tw_938/ee939dca2723e809e69fe02048a2643a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FHd02KroxPGWcMZWKoNRliA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnews_tvbs_com_tw_938%2Fee939dca2723e809e69fe02048a2643a&h=ccb72f2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n殺人犯的魅力在哪？美國一名33歲男子瓦茲(Christopher Watts)因出軌而謀殺懷有身孕的妻子，以及兩名女兒，上月被判終身監禁，目前正在監獄服刑，但詭異的是，在他坐牢期間，全美各地竟然湧入了情書，向他示愛。<br />\n<br />\n來自科羅拉多州(Colorado)的瓦茲，日前殘忍殺害孕妻莎娜(Shanann Watts)及2名女兒塞萊斯特(Celeste)和貝拉(Bella)，他原先虛情假意在媒體上表示「妻女是他的生命，希望她們平安回來」，不過警方隨後在他任職的石油公司油桶中發現3人遺體，拆穿他的假面具，今年8月將他逮捕入獄。<br />\n<br />\n不過，就在瓦茲坐牢期間，大量情書竟蜂擁而至。署名Candace的女性便寄了好幾封情書給他，信中寫著，「我很在乎你(不要問我為什麼)，可能我瘋了...我非常想了解你...若你回信給我，我將是全世界最快樂的女孩。」<br />\n<br />\n不只在美國，來自澳洲的凱特(Kate)更對他吐露愛意，「你是我看過擁有最善良臉龐的人」，隨信還附上幾張自己的照片。<br />\n<br />\n對於這種現象，德薩爾斯大學的法證心理學教授蘭斯蘭(Katherine Ramsland)指，在極少數情況下，女性可能會因為男性犯下暴力行為而出現性興奮，是「接近暴力的刺激因素」，而更常見的是女性相信可以馴服他們，「用愛來修復這些男人。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BB%96%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%86%E5%AD%95%E5%A6%BB%E8%B7%9F%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%A9-%E7%AB%9F%E7%84%B6%E6%94%B6%E5%88%B0%E5%85%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%83%85%E6%9B%B8-053126948.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BB%2596%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E4%25BA%2586%25E5%25AD%2595%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E8%25B7%259F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25A9-%25E7%25AB%259F%25E7%2584%25B6%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%259B%25B8-053126948.html&d=71pwVW65x16IUdXCvZTcCB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=20bb24f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BB%96%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%86%E5%AD%95%E5%A6%BB%E8%B7%9F%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%A9-%E7%AB%9F%E7%84%B6%E6%94%B6%E5%88%B0%E5%85%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%83%85%E6%9B%B8-053126948.html</a><br />\n<br />\n求助熱線：<br />\n<br />\n風雨蘭<br />\n<br />\n2375 5322<br />\n<br />\n東華三院芷若園危機介入及支援中心<br />\n<br />\n18281<br />\n<br />\n和諧之家<br />\n<br />\n2522 0434　（婦女24小時求助熱線）<br />\n<br />\n2295 1386　（男士求助熱線）<br />\n<br />\n護苗基金兒童性侵犯熱線<br />\n<br />\n2889 9933　（星期一至星期五　上午10時至下午6時）"},{"pid":"e93950a90828e9c8b42a041d16e2de33c959944f","tid":958579,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:39:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4dacfb1c151f74dc04f3996a891e657d0813207d","tid":958579,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc917b6b50e1b5abfd72237e1d64bdef358ea04","tid":958579,"uid":27482,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:40:55.000Z","msg":"又證明男人唔壞女人唔愛"},{"pid":"b5929fb738f2f17dfc832dcc4406638d4383c53e","tid":958579,"uid":73627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:41:46.000Z","msg":"Mです"},{"pid":"260fdbb9bb033fafc7f42fd81582ed2af885b7a4","tid":958579,"uid":181527,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"7cc917b6b50e1b5abfd72237e1d64bdef358ea04","tid":958579,"uid":27482,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:40:55.000Z","msg":"又證明男人唔壞女人唔愛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:42:02.000Z","msg":"唔係因為佢殺人先愛<br />\n我諗純粹係因為佢生得靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7c3cd7c2d94f11b887796d3ab6ea9dc0275f93","tid":958579,"uid":42283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit